Headline: Winners all – Manila Bulletin
Text: The Manunuri ng Pelikulang Pilipino recently announced nominees for the 43rd Gawad Urian Awards slated October.It isn’t a surprise that many of those nominated are among the country’s more popular stars including Kathryn Bernardo, Nadine Lustre and Alden Richards. Of course, it goes without saying, they are all winners just by being merely nominated.Here’s the complete
